updates.update_content:
Hello!
@US backers: Thank you for your patience! I can see from social media that the US & Canadian rewards keep getting to their owners, and that's great!
I'm getting your tracking numbers from our fulfilment partner gradually, day after day, and I can safely say that half of the packages is out already. They weren't able to keep the alphabetical order after all - so sorry for misinforming you about it!
